{"id": "47f1ca439bcf75ad2b7f66531002df1ef8c65f34e5ebad75a00b57f33e5173f1", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:0", "text": "Calculates the cross product between two vectors. The cross product produces a resulting vector that is perpendicular to the two input vectors. This can be useful when trying to find the normal vector of a polygon if you use two input vectors in the polygon plane."}
{"id": "38584b10da8233a54a288d585135b46bf72933147d492442bbbea125750112b0", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:2", "text": "Vector 1"}
{"id": "cb9476332c7fcb5ad8763068ecf2a016a05b29f7977cb4d286610997fd39fe67", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:3", "text": "The first vector in the cross product calculation."}
{"id": "eace214ef9a6ada7f46d506e1df6221ea33bebac3749fc443319088cb847642b", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:4", "text": "Vector 2"}
{"id": "740aac13f098a21de204728c9e628d4cf0396cccb0380db11c4ce05d6d2a0e76", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:5", "text": "The second vector in the cross product calculation."}
{"id": "8a7fac9c892cf9041268ec1a6b37392025cf7e7c435a872bbeca59294b6eaca4", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:6", "text": "Normalize Result"}
{"id": "7743dd6559bbacd2a261f4f61e26cd8bdc60747aa360ac4eee17368e48d92455", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:7", "text": "When enabled (set to 1) the cross product result will be a normalized vector."}
{"id": "35f6e1ebb9b040db4e992f8d8fb554d4bc9ad8ea924c6744adc8ae3f58bc3498", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:9", "text": "resultXYZ"}
{"id": "5963b1cf571fb4aa47cd695b5f674b28f031f1c0c8ab5d65f15f05b794fc5ed6", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:10", "text": "The cross product result vector."}
{"id": "db7dd1ce0d7ea86988255ca35194b0f1bd3ac901a577cbf001917e21a93cd36c", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:11", "text": "resultX"}
{"id": "29ae71f9ed673ba0ac9f0665be3a580e22f3730cc133352d450ae293b0912204", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:12", "text": "The X component from the resultXYZ output."}
{"id": "1559ea0c7d8aa4ad51badbe1b30a3a5d7b82932753dbc63044d02897c487480c", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:13", "text": "resultY"}
{"id": "d123f179f225b75f5c31d8eb27e55d3e111c3dcb113e1b574dcb3c6f0d2e9162", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:14", "text": "The Y component from the resultXYZ output."}
{"id": "153df47561d2ede586a69b0186936cf344555bcbef47ecadd8fbf8b7ce5b2672", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:15", "text": "resultZ"}
{"id": "862a07bec45906d80eb88bd5c5e3e88c294baf8437e127dce1ee92ec7d457d62", "item_id": "8b0a79ce92:16", "text": "The Z component from the resultXYZ output."}
